OL,3,CPrivate school forced to close blames
OL,4,Cfalling numbers and rising fees
OL,6,FFormer pupils include singer Alison
OL,7,FGoldfrapp and country-pop twins
OL,8,FCatherine and Lizzy Ward Thomas.
OL,10,FThe decision follows the publication
OL,11,Fof the latest annual census from the
OL,12,FIndependent Schools Council (ISC)
OL,13,Fearlier this month which said the
OL,14,Fnumber of new pupils joining private
OL,15,Fschools has fallen by 2.7% in the last
OL,16,Fyear amid rising fees ` the biggest
OL,17,Ffall since data was first collected in
OL,18,F2011.
