OL,6,FA statement on the Alton School
OL,7,Fwebsite said the trustees had proposed
OL,8,Fthe school would close at the end of
OL,9,Fthe academic year and its nursery
OL,10,Fwould close on August 31.
OL,12,FThe statement said: "This proposal is
OL,13,Fbased on a continued decline in pupil
OL,14,Fnumbers, to the extent that the school
OL,15,Fhas now become unviable. This is due
OL,16,Fto a combination of adverse political
OL,17,Fand economic factors.
