OL,6,F"Our community has served Alton and
OL,7,Fthe surrounding area since 1938 and it
OL,8,Fis with deep sadness that we may be
OL,9,Funable to continue providing this
OL,10,Feducation in the future."
OL,12,FThe ISC census, based on a survey of
OL,13,F1,411 UK independent schools conducted
OL,14,Fin January, said the average fee for a
OL,15,Fday school ` which the majority of ISC
OL,16,Fpupils attend ` is now #6,021 per term
OL,17,For #18,064 per annum.
