OL,4,Cfalling numbers and rising fees
OL,6,FBoarding school fees are the highest
OL,7,Fat #14,153 a term on average, up 9% on
OL,8,Flast year, while day fees for boarding
OL,9,Fschool are #7,975, up 8.8% on last
OL,10,Fyear. Among day schools, the majority
OL,11,Fcharge between #3,000 and #6,000 a
OL,12,Fterm.
OL,14,FIn a foreword to the report, ISC
OL,15,Fchairman Barnaby Lenon said Labour's
OL,16,Fplan to charge 20% VAT on private fees
OL,17,Fis "looming large in parents' minds"
OL,18,Fand private schools are concerned
OL,19,Fabout pupil recruitment and retention.
