OL,6,FHe said: "A pupil bulge has made its
OL,7,Fway through the school system, but
OL,8,Findependent school numbers have not
OL,9,Fbeen rising to the same extent,
OL,10,Fleading to a decline in the proportion
OL,11,Fof children educated in independent
OL,12,Fschools from 7% to 6%."
OL,14,FMr Lenon warned that an increase in
OL,15,Ffees caused by VAT ` when combined
OL,16,Fwith high inflation and increased
OL,17,Femployer contributions to the
OL,18,FTeachers' Pension Scheme ` could
OL,19,Fprovide "a far more acute shock to the
OL,20,Fsystem".
